Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙已经找到…并且毁掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的双腿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大家出来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛雅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 爸爸 发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…在喝茶的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天文明也说会早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上马上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------13ED---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:30.57,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君だけのため　光る世界　ここにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:43.10,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}幼い手で握りしめてた　失くさないよ　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:52.42,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}真っ白な願いを　君と追いかけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:23:00.41,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}まだ迷い込む　寂しいげな夜だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:09.64,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}あの日の面影を　見つけで　思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:14.42,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がいるから　どこでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:18.67,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}何度、転んでも　笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:23.03,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然だとか　必然だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:26.06,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要らないほど　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:34.87,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと輝く　思い出なら　君の側にだけ　あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:43.29,13ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大切な世界　離さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:30.57,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仅属于你的光辉世界 就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:43.10,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握着你幼小的手 牢牢地不让它溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:52.42,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}纯白的心愿 与你共同追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:23:00.41,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若是被踌躇包围 寂寞如水的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:09.64,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}请于记忆深处 再次寻回 那天的音容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:14.42,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}因为有你在旁 不管身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:18.67,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使不断跌倒 也会笑着面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:23.03,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是偶然 还是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:26.06,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我已变得无比坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:34.87,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若能缔造闪耀回忆 必因有你在旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:43.29,13ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}最珍贵的世界 两手紧握 不再松开
